   826                                  ; =============================================================================
   827                                  ; s2_readline - Read one line from keyboard into [DI], max CX chars.
   828                                  ; Supports: Backspace, Delete, Enter, Left/Right cursor movement,
   829                                  ; Home/End, Up/Down history navigation.
   830                                  ; On entry: DI = buffer address, CX = max chars including room for null.
   831                                  ; On exit:  [DI] = null-terminated string.
